<subSubSection pageId="202" pageNumber="964" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="202.[166,1376,296,1042]" pageId="202" pageNumber="964">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[169,526,770,803]" pageId="202" pageNumber="964">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Recent taxonomic changes have substantially reduced distribution of the Burmese Whiskered 
<taxonomicName authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[170,263,849,882]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="202" pageNumber="964" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
, and its conservationsstatus is in need of revision. It is currently known from relatively few specimens over a relatively wide area, but virtually nothing is known aboutits ecology and threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
